3. Apply the following styles to all web pages of online book store web application.
a. Fonts and Styles: font-family, font-style, font-weight and font-size
b. Backgrounds and colors: color, background-color, background-image and
background-repeat
c. Text: text-decoration, text-transformation, text-align and text-indentation, textalign
d. Borders: border, border-width, border-color and border-style
e. Styles for links: A: link, A: visited, A: active, A: hover
f. Selectors, Classes, Layers and Positioning elements.



.th
{
font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size-adjust:0.75;
font-weight:bolder;
}
p.style
{
font-style:oblique;
font-weight:200;
}
a:link
{
color:green;
font-family:"Arial";
}
a:visited
{
color:blue;
}
a:hover
{
color:pink;
}
a:active
{
color:red;
font-family:"Palantino Linotype";
}
.borer
{
border-width:10px;
border-color:grey grey grey red;
border-style:solid;
text-align: left;
text-indent: 50px;
text-transform: uppercase;
}
